			<!-- </div>  -->
</div>
<br><br>
<div class="container-fluid main">
	<div class="scroll-to"></div>
		<div id="explanation-area">
			<div class="row-fluid stripe2">
				<div class="fluid-center">
					<h4>Let's say you're <span class="label label-large label-info label-scenario">looking for a job </span> on the internet. Perhaps you're <span class="label label-large label-info label-scenario">buying</span> a very specific vintage car, maybe even a house. What if you're a musician <span class="label label-large label-info label-scenario">waiting for a bargain</span> on a used drumset?</h4>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row-fluid stripe3">
				<div class="fluid-center">
					<h4>You keep refreshing your ads sites, forums, bulletin boards and looking if there's anything new that suits you. Weekly, daily, even hourly.</h4>

					<!-- <h3>This is...</h3> -->
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row-fluid stripe4">
				<div class="fluid-center">
					<div class="span4 pagination-centered text-center">
					<h3>Time consuming!</h3>
					</div>
					<div class="span4 pagination-centered text-center">
						<div class="jeez"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="span4 pagination-centered text-center">
						<h3 class="little-down">Boring!</h3>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row-fluid stripe5">
				<div class="fluid-center pagination-centered text-center">
					<h2 class="bit-bigger">The Butler works for you.</h2>
					<br>
					<div class = "neki">
						<div class="span4 pagination-centered text-center">
							<div class="box">
								<div class="circle pagination-centered text-center"><h4 class="number1">1</h4></div>
								<div class="instruction">
									<span class="instruction-title text-center">Insert keywords</span>
									<br><br>
									Put in your keywords that you wish our Butler to monitor (e.g. ford mustang)
									<div class="keywords-image"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="span4 pagination-centered text-center">
							<div class="box">
								<div class="circle pagination-centered text-center"><h4 class="number">2</h4></div>
								<div class="instruction">
									<span class="instruction-title text-center">Insert URLs</span>
									<br><br>
									Put in the websites where you expect your keywords to show up in the future (e.g. some_domain/used_cars)
									<div class="urls-image"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="span4 pagination-centered text-center">
							<div class="box">
								<div class="circle pagination-centered text-center"><h4 class="number">3</h4></div>
								<div class="instruction">
									<span class="instruction-title text-center">Forget about it!</span>
									<br><br>
									The Butler will inform you immediately when he finds something new!
									<div class="wait-image"></div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- <ul>
						<li>1. You put in your keywords (e.g. ford mustang)</li>
						<li>2. You put in the websites where you expect your keywords to show up in the future (e.g. http://oldtimers.com/forum/used_cars)</li>
						<li>3. The Keyword Butler will inform you immediately when he finds something new!</li>
					</ul> -->
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row-fluid stripe6">
						<div class="fluid-center">
								<!--<div class="jw-image"> -->
								
						</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>


